<TITLE> Barca defender Abidal out for eight weeks </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 MADRID, Feb 22 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) -Barcelona defender Eric Abidal is expected to be out of action for about eight weeks with a torn groin muscle, the Primera Liga club said on Saturday. The French international had to be substituted in the first half of Barca's 2-1 home defeat by city rivals Espanyol, after getting injured in a challenge with Sergio Sanchez. The club's medical team said they would carry out further tests on Sunday and if the nature of the injury is confirmed he would not return to action until the end of April. He will miss Barcelona's trip to Olympique Lyon in the Champions League first knockout round on Tuesda
